Conclusion
This project introduces career intelligence as a retention strategy. Unlike which predicts who might leave, this project explains why employees may eventually disengage by uncovering promotion gaps and career stagnation patterns. By identifying retention opportunities early, Palo Alto Networks can move from reactive retention to proactive career-centric workforce management, making this project clearly distinct in prediction goal, methodology, and business value.

